snippet.title: Woman in Australia appears to drive straight through Covid-19 checkpoint
snippet.description:
A Melbourne woman has caused outrage after apparently travelling through a coronavirus checkpoint while refusing to answer questions from police.

In a video posted to Facebook, Eve Black is seen behind the wheel of a vehicle as she appears to travel towards a police checkpoint.

When she stops, she tells the office that she “doesn’t need to answer” his questions.

After driving off, Ms Black is seen celebrating, saying: “I feel so good!”

The video has been seen thousands of times, with many social media users criticising her behaviour.
